    "Both sides naturally form a battleground, where the attackers operate the generation, and the defenders perform the detection.",
    "Indeed, this incessant dispute is what pushes the topic forward and enhances its remarkable progress.",
    "The study of deepfakes has gained a lot of attention in recent years and the number of publications is increasing exponentially since the first works dating back to 2016.",
